---
title: Chicken and Pineapple Mini Quesadillas with Green Bell Pepper & Lime Crema
description: If you thought sweet and savoury combos were delicious, prepare to be blown away by this chicken and pineapple quesadilla, co-starring green bell pepper! A zesty lime crema elevates this dish to a new family favourite!
